---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="AIGIS by Levenhall — The system of record for AI governance" description="Prove your AI is compliant in every jurisdiction you operate in. Inventory, map, test, and prove — audit-ready evidence for the EU AI Act, NIST AI RMF, Colorado SB 205, NYC LL 144, and every framework in between.">

    <!-- ── HERO ── -->
    <section class="a-hero">
        <div class="a-hero-glow"></div>
        <div class="a-hero-grid"></div>
        <div class="a-hero-stage">
            <p class="a-hero-tag">A Levenhall Product</p>
            <img src="/images/products/aigis-lockup.png" alt="AIGIS by Levenhall" class="a-hero-lockup">
            <h1 class="a-hero-h1">Prove your AI is compliant.<br/>In every jurisdiction you operate in.</h1>
            <p class="a-hero-tagline">AIGIS is the system of record for AI governance. Inventory your AI systems, map them to the regulations that apply, run the regulator's own tests, and produce audit-ready evidence &mdash; so compliance is defensible, not a spreadsheet.</p>
            <div class="a-hero-cta">
                <a href="https://aigis.levenhall.com/register" class="btn btn-gold" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Request Access</a>
                <a href="https://aigis.levenhall.com/demo" class="btn btn-outline-white" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">See the Interactive Demo</a>
            </div>
            <p class="a-hero-meta">Live at <a href="https://aigis.levenhall.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">aigis.levenhall.com</a></p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── REGISTRY EXAMPLE ── -->
    <section class="a-registry">
        <div class="a-reg-grid">
            <div class="a-reg-copy reveal">
                <span class="a-eyebrow">§ AI System Registry</span>
                <h2>Every AI system, every jurisdiction, every regulator's test.</h2>
                <p>The registry is the spine of the platform. Register every AI system in production &mdash; internal models, vendor systems, GenAI &mdash; and AIGIS classifies risk tier, auto-maps the obligations that apply, and runs the tests the regulator would run. When the auditor knocks, the evidence is already there.</p>
            </div>
            <aside class="a-reg-card reveal">
                <div class="a-reg-head">
                    <div>
                        <span class="a-reg-name">Loan Underwriting Model</span>
                        <span class="a-reg-cat">Credit &amp; Lending &middot; EU &middot; NYC &middot; Colorado</span>
                    </div>
                    <span class="a-reg-tier">High risk</span>
                </div>
                <div class="a-reg-block">
                    <span class="a-reg-block-label">Regulatory mapping</span>
                    <ul class="a-reg-maps">
                        <li><span class="a-reg-map">EU AI Act — Art. 9</span><span class="a-status a-status-ok">Compliant</span></li>
                        <li><span class="a-reg-map">EU AI Act — Art. 10</span><span class="a-status a-status-warn">In progress</span></li>
                        <li><span class="a-reg-map">Colorado SB 205</span><span class="a-status a-status-ok">Compliant</span></li>
                        <li><span class="a-reg-map">NYC Local Law 144</span><span class="a-status a-status-fail">Non-compliant</span></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="a-reg-block">
                    <span class="a-reg-block-label">Latest bias test</span>
                    <div class="a-reg-bias">
                        <span class="a-bias-val">DI 0.66</span>
                        <span class="a-bias-fail">FAIL</span>
                    </div>
                    <span class="a-bias-detail">female 41% vs male 62% selection</span>
                </div>
            </aside>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── ONE PLATFORM · EVERY FRAMEWORK ── -->
    <section class="a-frameworks">
        <div class="a-frameworks-inner reveal">
            <span class="a-eyebrow a-eyebrow-cyan">§ One platform &middot; every framework</span>
            <h2>The regulations, mapped once.</h2>
            <p class="a-frameworks-lede">Frameworks are added and updated by Levenhall's regulatory team. You classify the system once. The mapping travels with it.</p>
            <div class="a-fw-grid">
                <div class="a-fw"><span class="a-fw-region">EU</span><span class="a-fw-name">EU AI Act</span></div>
                <div class="a-fw"><span class="a-fw-region">US</span><span class="a-fw-name">NIST AI RMF</span></div>
                <div class="a-fw"><span class="a-fw-region">US · CO</span><span class="a-fw-name">Colorado SB 205</span></div>
                <div class="a-fw"><span class="a-fw-region">US · NYC</span><span class="a-fw-name">NYC Local Law 144</span></div>
                <div class="a-fw"><span class="a-fw-region">CA</span><span class="a-fw-name">Canada AIDA</span></div>
                <div class="a-fw"><span class="a-fw-region">UK</span><span class="a-fw-name">UK AI Principles</span></div>
                <div class="a-fw"><span class="a-fw-region">SG</span><span class="a-fw-name">Singapore Model AI</span></div>
                <div class="a-fw"><span class="a-fw-region">AU</span><span class="a-fw-name">Australia AI Ethics</span></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── THE PLATFORM (4 STEPS) ── -->
    <section class="a-platform">
        <div class="a-plat-grid">
            <aside class="a-plat-rail reveal">
                <span class="a-eyebrow">§ The platform</span>
                <h2>Four steps.<br/>Four proofs.</h2>
                <ol class="a-plat-toc">
                    <li><span>01</span>Inventory</li>
                    <li><span>02</span>Map</li>
                    <li><span>03</span>Test</li>
                    <li><span>04</span>Prove</li>
                </ol>
            </aside>
            <div class="a-plat-body">
                <article class="a-plat-step reveal">
                    <span class="a-plat-num">01</span>
                    <div>
                        <h3>Inventory</h3>
                        <p>Register every AI or ML system in production &mdash; internal, vendor, GenAI. Owner, purpose, data source, deployment context, jurisdiction of use.</p>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article class="a-plat-step reveal">
                    <span class="a-plat-num">02</span>
                    <div>
                        <h3>Map</h3>
                        <p>AIGIS classifies risk tier and auto-maps obligations across every market the system touches &mdash; article by article, control by control &mdash; using the regulatory graph maintained by Levenhall.</p>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article class="a-plat-step reveal">
                    <span class="a-plat-num">03</span>
                    <div>
                        <h3>Test</h3>
                        <p>Run the tests the regulator runs: bias and disparate impact, robustness, toxicity, hallucination, data provenance. Automated where the regulator accepts automation, routed for human review where it doesn't.</p>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article class="a-plat-step reveal">
                    <span class="a-plat-num">04</span>
                    <div>
                        <h3>Prove</h3>
                        <p>Generate the artefacts the board, the underwriter, and the regulator ask for: technical documentation, conformance reports, incident logs, an audit-ready evidence pack that maps to each obligation.</p>
                    </div>
                </article>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── COVERAGE ── -->
    <section class="a-coverage">
        <div class="a-cov-inner reveal">
            <span class="a-eyebrow a-eyebrow-cyan">§ Coverage</span>
            <h2>Every market that regulates AI.</h2>
            <div class="a-cov-grid">
                <div class="a-cov-region">
                    <span class="a-cov-flag">🇺🇸 🇨🇦</span>
                    <h4>North America</h4>
                    <p>EU AI Act readiness for North American exporters, Colorado SB 205, NYC Local Law 144, Canada AIDA, NIST AI RMF.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="a-cov-region">
                    <span class="a-cov-flag">🇪🇺 🇬🇧</span>
                    <h4>Europe</h4>
                    <p>EU AI Act (full title mapping), UK AI Principles and member-state guidance.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="a-cov-region">
                    <span class="a-cov-flag">🇦🇺 🇳🇿</span>
                    <h4>Australia &amp; NZ</h4>
                    <p>Australia AI Ethics Principles, New Zealand Algorithm Charter.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="a-cov-region">
                    <span class="a-cov-flag">🇸🇬 🇯🇵 🇰🇷</span>
                    <h4>Asia</h4>
                    <p>Singapore Model AI Governance, Japan and South Korea guidance, more added continuously.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── PROTECT YOUR AI (INSURANCE) ── -->
    <section class="a-insurance">
        <div class="a-ins-grid">
            <div class="a-ins-copy reveal">
                <span class="a-eyebrow">§ Protect your AI</span>
                <h2>The AI you can prove is the AI you can insure.</h2>
                <p>AIGIS matches your evaluation record against the AI insurance market. Twenty-four carriers, four live feeds, eight partner feeds. Get an insurability score based on the same evidence your regulator will see.</p>
                <p>For underwriters, the record is a continuous signal to price against. For brokers, a defensible file at renewal. For the enterprise, coverage that doesn't require a fire drill every quarter.</p>
            </div>
            <aside class="a-ins-card reveal">
                <div class="a-ins-head">
                    <span class="a-ins-score">72<span class="a-ins-of">/100</span></span>
                    <span class="a-ins-verdict">Insurable</span>
                </div>
                <div class="a-ins-block">
                    <span class="a-ins-block-label">Coverage categories</span>
                    <ul>
                        <li>AI Liability &amp; E&amp;O</li>
                        <li>Algorithmic Bias &amp; Discrimination</li>
                        <li>Regulatory Defense &amp; Penalty</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="a-ins-block">
                    <span class="a-ins-block-label">Matched carriers</span>
                    <ul class="a-carriers">
                        <li><span>Armilla AI</span><span class="a-c-pct">99%</span></li>
                        <li><span>Coalition</span><span class="a-c-pct">99%</span></li>
                        <li><span>Counterpart</span><span class="a-c-pct">99%</span></li>
                        <li><span>Relm Insurance</span><span class="a-c-pct">96%</span></li>
                        <li><span>Resilience</span><span class="a-c-pct">96%</span></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </aside>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── CTA ── -->
    <section class="a-cta">
        <div class="a-cta-glow"></div>
        <div class="a-cta-inner">
            <div class="a-cta-rule"></div>
            <p class="a-cta-eyebrow">Live Now &middot; v2026.06</p>
            <h2>Built for regulated enterprises.<br/>Financial services, insurance, healthcare.</h2>
            <p>Request access to the platform, or step through an industry-specific walkthrough of the interactive demo.</p>
            <div class="btn-group" style="justify-content: center;">
                <a href="https://aigis.levenhall.com/register" class="btn btn-gold" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Request Access</a>
                <a href="https://aigis.levenhall.com/demo" class="btn btn-outline-white" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">See the Demo</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
    /* ── HERO ── */
    .a-hero {
        background:
            radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 50% 50%, rgba(56, 217, 201, 0.06), transparent 70%),
            radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 50% at 50% 0%, rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.08), transparent 60%),
            #04070e;
        padding: var(--s-16) var(--s-3) var(--s-12);
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
    }

    .a-hero-glow {
        position: absolute;
        top: 50%; left: 50%;
        width: 800px; height: 800px;
        transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
        background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(56, 217, 201, 0.14) 0%, transparent 60%);
        filter: blur(50px);
        pointer-events: none;
    }

    .a-hero-grid {
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        background-image:
            linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.012) 1px, transparent 1px),
            linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.012) 1px, transparent 1px);
        background-size: 64px 64px;
        pointer-events: none;
        mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, black 25%, transparent 75%);
        -webkit-mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, black 25%, transparent 75%);
    }

    .a-hero::after {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
        height: 1px;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(56, 217, 201, 0.5), transparent);
        opacity: 0.55;
    }

    .a-hero-stage {
        text-align: center;
        max-width: 720px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
    }

    .a-hero-tag {
        font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 0.66rem;
        letter-spacing: 3.5px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--gold);
        margin-bottom: var(--s-4);
    }

    .a-hero-lockup {
        max-width: 380px;
        width: 90%;
        height: auto;
        margin: 0 auto var(--s-6);
        display: block;
        filter: brightness(0) invert(1) drop-shadow(0 0 30px rgba(56, 217, 201, 0.2));
    }

    .a-hero-h1 {
        font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 4vw, 2.9rem);
        line-height: 1.15;
        color: #fff;
        margin: 0 0 var(--s-4);
        letter-spacing: -0.8px;
    }

    .a-hero-tagline {
        font-family: 'Georgia', 'Times New Roman', serif;
        font-size: 1.05rem;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65);
        line-height: 1.75;
        max-width: 620px;
        margin: 0 auto var(--s-5);
    }

    .a-hero-cta {
        display: flex;
        gap: var(--s-2);
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        justify-content: center;
        margin-bottom: var(--s-3);
    }

    .a-hero-meta {
        font-family: 'SF Mono', 'Menlo', monospace;
        font-size: 0.78rem;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
        letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }

    .a-hero-meta a { color: rgba(56, 217, 201, 0.85); text-decoration: none; }

    /* ── SHARED ── */
    .a-eyebrow {
        display: block;
        font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 0.7rem;
        letter-spacing: 2.5px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--gold);
        margin-bottom: var(--s-4);
    }

    .a-eyebrow-cyan { color: rgba(56, 217, 201, 0.85); }

    .a-registry h2,
    .a-frameworks h2,
    .a-platform h2,
    .a-coverage h2,
    .a-insurance h2,
    .a-cta h2 {
        font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
        font-weight: 600;
        letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    }

    /* ── REGISTRY ── */
    .a-registry {
        background: var(--cream);
        padding: var(--s-16) 0;
    }

    .a-reg-grid {
        max-width: 1080px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 var(--s-3);
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        gap: var(--s-10);
        align-items: center;
    }

    .a-reg-copy h2 {
        font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3vw, 2.4rem);
        color: var(--deep-navy);
        margin: 0 0 var(--s-5);
        line-height: 1.18;
    }

    .a-reg-copy p {
        font-size: 1.05rem;
        line-height: 1.85;
        color: var(--text-medium);
    }

    .a-reg-card {
        background: #fff;
        border: 1px solid var(--border-warm);
        border-top: 3px solid rgba(56, 217, 201, 0.8);
        padding: var(--s-5);
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: var(--s-4);
    }

    .a-reg-head {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: flex-start;
        gap: var(--s-3);
        padding-bottom: var(--s-3);
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-warm);
    }

    .a-reg-name {
        display: block;
        font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 1.15rem;
        color: var(--deep-navy);
        letter-spacing: -0.3px;
        margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
    }

    .a-reg-cat {
        display: block;
        font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        color: var(--text-medium);
    }

    .a-reg-tier {
        font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
        font-size: 0.68rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 1.5px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--burgundy);
        background: var(--burgundy-surface);
        border: 1px solid rgba(139, 21, 56, 0.2);
        padding: 0.3rem 0.6rem;
        white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .a-reg-block-label {
        display: block;
        font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
        font-size: 0.62rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 2px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--text-medium);
        margin-bottom: var(--s-2);
    }

    .a-reg-maps {
        list-style: none;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
    }

    .a-reg-maps li {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        gap: var(--s-2);
        padding: 0.55rem 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(30, 58, 95, 0.06);
    }

    .a-reg-maps li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

    .a-reg-map {
        font-family: 'SF Mono', 'Menlo', monospace;
        font-size: 0.82rem;
        color: var(--deep-navy);
    }

    .a-status {
        font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
        font-size: 0.66rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        padding: 0.22rem 0.5rem;
        white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .a-status-ok { color: #2a8c5e; background: rgba(42, 140, 94, 0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(42, 140, 94, 0.25); }
    .a-status-warn { color: #a17a2a; background: rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.15); border: 1px solid rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.35); }
    .a-status-fail { color: #b1315b; background: rgba(139, 21, 56, 0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(139, 21, 56, 0.3); }

    .a-reg-bias {
        display: flex;
        align-items: baseline;
        gap: var(--s-3);
        margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    }

    .a-bias-val {
        font-family: 'SF Mono', 'Menlo', monospace;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--deep-navy);
        letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    }

    .a-bias-fail {
        font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
        font-size: 0.7rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 1.5px;
        color: #b1315b;
        background: rgba(139, 21, 56, 0.1);
        border: 1px solid rgba(139, 21, 56, 0.3);
        padding: 0.25rem 0.55rem;
    }

    .a-bias-detail {
        font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
        font-size: 0.82rem;
        color: var(--text-medium);
        font-style: italic;
    }

    /* ── FRAMEWORKS ── */
    .a-frameworks {
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, #0a1628 0%, var(--deep-navy) 100%);
        padding: var(--s-16) 0;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
    }

    .a-frameworks::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
        height: 1px;
        background: rgba(56, 217, 201, 0.3);
    }

    .a-frameworks-inner {
        max-width: 900px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 var(--s-3);
        text-align: center;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
    }

    .a-frameworks-inner h2 {
        font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.4vw, 2.6rem);
        line-height: 1.15;
        color: #fff;
        margin: 0 0 var(--s-4);
    }

    .a-frameworks-lede {
        font-family: 'Georgia', 'Times New Roman', serif;
        font-size: 1.05rem;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
        line-height: 1.75;
        margin: 0 auto var(--s-8);
        max-width: 640px;
    }

    .a-fw-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
        gap: var(--s-2);
    }

    .a-fw {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
        border-top: 2px solid rgba(56, 217, 201, 0.5);
        padding: var(--s-4) var(--s-3);
        text-align: left;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 0.35rem;
    }

    .a-fw-region {
        font-family: 'SF Mono', 'Menlo', monospace;
        font-size: 0.65rem;
        letter-spacing: 1.5px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: rgba(56, 217, 201, 0.8);
    }

    .a-fw-name {
        font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        color: #fff;
    }

    /* ── PLATFORM (4 STEPS) ── */
    .a-platform {
        background: var(--stone);
        padding: var(--s-16) 0;
    }

    .a-plat-grid {
        max-width: 1080px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 var(--s-3);
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 0.85fr 1.4fr;
        gap: var(--s-10);
        align-items: start;
    }

    .a-plat-rail {
        position: sticky;
        top: 100px;
        padding-right: var(--s-3);
    }

    .a-plat-rail h2 {
        font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.4vw, 2.5rem);
        line-height: 1.1;
        color: var(--deep-navy);
        margin: 0 0 var(--s-5);
    }

    .a-plat-toc {
        list-style: none;
        margin: var(--s-5) 0 0;
        padding: 0;
        border-top: 1px solid rgba(30, 58, 95, 0.12);
    }

    .a-plat-toc li {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 40px 1fr;
        gap: var(--s-2);
        padding: 0.65rem 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(30, 58, 95, 0.08);
        font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        color: var(--text-medium);
    }

    .a-plat-toc li span {
        font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
        font-style: italic;
        font-size: 1rem;
        color: var(--gold);
    }

    .a-plat-step {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 48px 1fr;
        gap: var(--s-5);
        padding-bottom: var(--s-6);
        margin-bottom: var(--s-6);
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(30, 58, 95, 0.1);
    }

    .a-plat-step:last-of-type { border-bottom: none; margin-bottom: 0; padding-bottom: 0; }

    .a-plat-num {
        font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
        font-style: italic;
        font-weight: 500;
